# ATP Tennis Match Analysis

## Introduction

I was curious about what factors influence outcomes in professional tennis matches. Specifically, I wanted to explore whether tournament importance, playing surface, and betting odds reveal patterns about competitiveness and predictability.

---

## Question 1: Which surfaces are used most often?

```malloy
run: matches -> {
  group_by: Surface
  aggregate: match_count
  order_by: match_count desc
}
